@thesolaceproject/livekit-components-solid

This package is a SolidJS port of @livekit/components-react v2.9.21
(https://github.com/livekit/components-js), Copyright LiveKit, Inc.,
licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

The framework-agnostic state logic comes from @livekit/components-core
(consumed as a regular npm dependency, not vendored). The hooks and
components in this package were translated from React (useState/useEffect)
to SolidJS (signals/effects) primitives; the observable wiring, visualizer
animation sequences, and component semantics follow the upstream source.
